    "If `verdict = SIGNAL_SURVIVES_FIXED_W_REWINDOWING`, the Quran's 5-D fingerprint is NOT an artefact of canonical surah boundaries; the same separation appears under a uniform-W segmentation. This is the strongest defence against the reviewer's worry.",
